schools.name: D L Dusty Dickens Elementary School

data.description:
Wonderful , Almost 2000 sq ft, two story, 4 bedroom, 3 bath (one bedroom/one bath downstairs) granite countertops, pantry with plenty of room for large kitchen table.  Upstairs has a large primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings, primary bathroom has separate shower and separate bathtub, double sinks and large walk in closet.  There is also a large loft and two other secondary bedrooms in the front.  Well appointed floor plan, the home has plenty of natural light, two car garage, large covered patio, large park across the street.  Great location, near the VA Hospital, shopping, schools, parks and highway access (215N & 15N).  Easy to maintain exterior!  A must see, traditional sale,  
move in ready and seller looking for a quick close.
